  "body": "As discussed in https://github.com/kubernetes/apiextensions-apiserver/issues/4 and on Slack with @sttts, @nikhita and @colemickens, it'd be good to have a sample-controller example repository to go along with the current `k8s.io/sample-apiserver` repo.\r\n\r\nIt could show how to properly use the `k8s.io/code-generator` repository to generate code for CRD types, and how to set up a basic workqueue and sync controller. This could then be used as a basis/reference for others looking to built their own extensions.\r\n",
